Name: Wool Control Center
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Description: Redesigns iOS 16 Control Center modules with realistic 3D wool and felt backgrounds. Includes global and per-module wool palettes, solid backgrounds, custom photos, opacity, texture density, depth, and corner radius controls.
